{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we couldn't take-- our things, yes-- but not furniture or anything of this sort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we moved to grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, second thing was that I couldn't go to school anymore, which-- I loved school, and the principal said if I have some friends, let them bring me homework.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had all the books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can study.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then very soon, they start preparing for ghetto, to put all the Jews in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they picked the worst part of the city with the oldest houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But Jews could live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So since my grandfather had still property outside of the city, we went there, except grandfather, knowing that this will be taken away, it's going to be Jewish, went to a lawyer who put date three weeks before the war, and he gave it to a mayor of that little town.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when we came in, the guy gave us half of the house, which the whole thing anyway was my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he opened it, and he said, stay with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we stayed there until we had to move to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nobody could stay over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We-- now, the funny part was that actually, my grandfather was an American citizen because his father was a citizen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was here, and his brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, my father's family, his much older brother and two sister, were also here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had the papers, which they didn't recognize.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some people were buying themself paper which were recognized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know why ours weren't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we had to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when we moved from Cracow to the suburbs, we could take some furniture with us, although that was already not ours.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
